    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "It seems like even a tiny bit of debris can cause a huge problem for the pilot. Is there any way to predict when these things might happen, or is it just one of those things where you have to constantly check the equipment during pre-flight?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
